live for... I'm so finished...

210
00:15:06,708 --> 00:15:07,833
Oh, can the melodrama

211
00:15:07,916 --> 00:15:09,666
and get your butt to class,
why don't you?

212
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:12,625
