you think it doesn't?

214
00:15:15,083 --> 00:15:17,791
Wait, wait...! Stop...! Help!!

215
00:15:22,208 --> 00:15:25,208
Well, this is it...
I'm through hoping for love...

216
00:15:25,291 --> 00:15:28,041
