here was to be with Tenma...

217
00:15:28,416 --> 00:15:29,750
I won't miss it...

218
00:15:29,833 --> 00:15:33,375
Hey... Harima... what
happened to the arm, big guy?

219
00:15:33,458 --> 00:15:35,041
